<p class="text-base-dark text-uppercase margin-top-2 margin-bottom-1"><strong>Self-assessment</strong></p>

<h1 class="font-heading-2xl">Tell us about your situation</h1>

<p class="font-serif-md margin-top-2 margin-bottom-3">
  You may be eligible for an exemption from Community Engagement activity reporting requirements if you meet certain criteria. If you qualify for an exemption, you will need to provide supporting documents.
</p>

<h2 class="margin-top-4 margin-bottom-2">Since the start date of the current reporting period, have you...</h2>

<div class="margin-bottom-2">
  <p class="margin-bottom-1"><strong>→ Had a serious medical condition</strong></p>
  <p class="font-serif-md text-base-dark">
    A physical or mental health issue that limits your ability to work or participate in activities
  </p>
</div>

<div class="margin-bottom-2">
  <p class="margin-bottom-1"><strong>→ Been treated for a substance-use disorder</strong></p>
  <p class="font-serif-md text-base-dark">
    Receiving treatment or in recovery from substance use that limits your ability to work or participate in activities
  </p>
</div>

<div class="margin-bottom-3">
  <p class="margin-bottom-1"><strong>→ Been released from jail or prison</strong></p>
  <p class="font-serif-md text-base-dark">
    Released from incarceration within the last 30 days
  </p>
</div>

<p class="font-serif-md margin-top-4 margin-bottom-4">
  If so, you may be eligible for an exemption to Community Engagement activity reporting requirements. If not, you will need to report your Community Engagement activities.
</p>

<div class="margin-top-4">
  <a href="#" class="usa-button">Apply for an exemption</a>
  <a href="#" class="usa-button usa-button--outline">Report activities</a>
</div>
